{"tid":2094344,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"請即致電: 3679 0242 !","createTime":"2020-07-04T14:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T02:36:11.000Z","uid":85751,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"399c1ee05fb596fd7930276575ee31db7cf204cf","tid":2094344,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:26:29.000Z","msg":"文宣都被打壓，香港人的創意又係時候要進化<br />\n<br />\n街上的傳單，燈柱上的電話，未曾見過俾撕紙狗撕<br />\n<br />\n何不利用呢樣 template??<br />\n<br />\n如:<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前有願榮光變數字歌，一切都係廣東話音調幫大手<br />\n<br />\n香港文化，好大部分都係廣東話文化，我哋要好好使用，做好長期抗爭的覺悟<br />\n<br />\n文宣手足每日驚俾人打，俾人拉都要出，為咩？為咗令社會熱度繼續，令大家知道身邊有同路人<br />\n<br />\n過咗一年有多，要醒一早醒，唔醒就點都唔醒<br />\n唔好靠文宣上資料去喚醒<br />\n係要散播，感染大眾，你每日都活在白色恐怖<br />\n請大眾自覺<br />\n<br />\n做大黃圈，唔只經濟，係社會風氣<br />\n<br />\n不是有希望才堅持，因為堅持才有希望。<br />\n<br />\n3679 0242!!"},{"pid":"10202cebabc8e971d50d29bf676a22308e1a9f6e","tid":2094344,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:27:32.000Z","msg":"文宣，粉飾太平<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072109</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57f6aaa5065122b58a510072bc217ce1d15e3473","tid":2094344,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:28:00.000Z","msg":"當一切有關香港事物，都是顛覆國家時<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2089906\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2089906</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3ca9a1b75425f2af1450eb84294fb840ad2c183","tid":2094344,"uid":55851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2a17ff0cf3d7023d4e2c2ce38688f4db466f8ef","tid":2094344,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"